<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Account Approved</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #006837;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777777;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #006837;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>ACPN Ota Zone</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <h2>Account Approved!</h2>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your ACPN Ota Zone account has been
          approved by an administrator. You can now log in to access all member
          features and benefits.</p>

        <a href='{{loginUrl}}' class='button'>Login to Your Account</a>

        <p>Thank you for your patience during the approval process. We look
          forward to your active participation in our community.</p>

        <p>Thank you,<br />ACPN Ota Zone Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>&copy;
          {{year}}
          Association of Community Pharmacists of Nigeria, Ota Zone. All rights
          reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>